response.original_title: Fighting for Peace in the Philippines: VICE News Interviews Nur Misuari
response.overview: "Nur Misuari is the founder of the Moro National Liberation Front (MNLF), an armed group that's fought for independence against the government of the Philippines for more than three decades.  "Misuari currently lives in a remote MNLF encampment on the island of Jolo. The area is a no-go zone for outsiders, especially journalists. VICE News takes the perilous journey into Jolo to meet Misuari and discuss the future of the MNLF as well as the current political situation in the Philippines."
response.title: Fighting for Peace in the Philippines: VICE News Interviews Nur Misuari
